{"tid":1387082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得應要為因示威而被捕甚至坐監既成立安家費基金","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T01:19:23.000Z","uid":73972,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fea16d3c626e15a1656545319253b80f9035e438","tid":1387082,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到有示威者俾人告暴動罪，真係好嬲，一班青年既大好前途咁就斷送左係班黑警到<br />\n<br />\n我明白有一班人好似我咁唔會衝前線或做犯法野，但如果你地真係有心支持呢個運動既，連捐少少錢，一千幾百都做唔到？等班示威者出黎都有筆錢傍身，移民又好，政治庇護又好<br />\n<br />\n基金由專業人士管理，所有支出收費收款都要留記錄，有audit，基金賠償會根據示威者被判刑期、原本職業學歷等因素考慮<br />\n<br />\n之前有人搞法律支援基金，有冇人可以幫手搞下呢個安家費基金？"},{"pid":"4c38798ddf3aeb7e5ae428ea43b640e1ecdb6552","tid":1387082,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"aad6cf32e5c64e98b62696e2c3453b3cf66128b7","tid":1387082,"uid":271953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:57:22.000Z","msg":"Support."},{"pid":"5ce333c5dbb3a73d17984bd9252e81bd9b0d8c91","tid":1387082,"uid":48490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3847e3390553e96d5997c9c5ae4587e882ccffe5","tid":1387082,"uid":48490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00918a4660821b9b67a266390896af5c513d99bb","tid":1387082,"uid":48490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8339e38b784990ffc93f41cab4e985c6bee42e6","tid":1387082,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cc7c2e0108181dae8d552310d38e53f6ce26f30","tid":1387082,"uid":81385,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:02:16.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n成事每月課金都得"},{"pid":"02386d79efd1d05f100b939466532c17566a5440","tid":1387082,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:03:23.000Z"